---
import BuildSquiggles from './BuildSquiggles.astro';
import GradientWrapper from './GradientWrapper.astro';
import Heading2 from './Heading2.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<section class="my-20 px-4 md:px-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div class="rounded-xl relative bg-white border-8 border-blue-950">
    <img
      src="/Squiggle-Pattern.svg"
      class="absolute -top-[8px] -right-[8px] w-40 invisible lg:visible"
    />
    <div class="p-8 md:py-12 lg:pr-[120px]">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="h-[256px] border-sky-600 border mb-4 lg:mb-0"></div>
        <div class="">
          <Heading2
            text="What Will You Build?"
            className="text-purple-500 mb-2 lg:mb-8"
          />
          <p class="text-xl mb-4">
            You'll learn strategies for modern web applications with Astro by
            building a few fully featured projects!
          </p>
          <ul
            class="text-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-between px-4 max-w-xl mx-auto"
          >
            <li>
              <Icon
                class="h-8 w-8 text-green-500 inline"
                pack="mdi"
                name="check-circle"
              /> blog
            </li>
            <li>
              <Icon
                class="h-8 w-8 text-green-500 inline"
                pack="mdi"
                name="check-circle"
              /> portfolio
            </li>
            <li>
              <Icon
                class="h-8 w-8 text-green-500 inline"
                pack="mdi"
                name="check-circle"
              /> more
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-cover bg-[url('/Navy-Circuit-Pattern.svg')] py-12 px-8 rounded-sm"
    >
      <p class="text-2xl text-center mb-8 font-bold text-white">
        Learn by building...
      </p>
      <ul
        class="mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-2 sm:gap-y-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 list-disc text-white pl-4 text-lg md:text-xl"
      >
        <li>Static vs Dynamic Routes</li>
        <li>SSG vs SSR</li>
        <li>Content Collections</li>
        <li>Astro Islands</li>
        <li>Image Optimization</li>
        <li>Integrations</li>
        <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li>Types with Zod</li>
        <li>API Endpoints</li>
        <li>Pagination</li>
        <li>Markdown and MDX</li>
        <li>SEO and Meta Tags</li>
        <li>RSS Feeds</li>
        <li>Deploying and Hosting</li>
        <li>Headless CMS</li>
      </ul>
      <!-- <p class="text-purple-600 italic text-center">
        *For a full list of all topics covered, see below at the video list!
      </p> -->
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
